In terms of ingredient type, carotenoids like lutein, zeaxanthin, and astaxanthin are gaining traction due to their antioxidant properties that help in neutralizing the harmful effects of blue light. The skincare segment holds a significant share in the market as consumers become more conscious about maintaining healthy skin in the digital age. Online retail channels are increasingly preferred for purchasing blue light protection products due to convenience and a wide range of product offerings.

